Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located in Lake Mary with proximity to numerous amenities including, restaurants, hotels, banking, and shopping.  Convenient access to I-4.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Attractive modern design. Constructed in 2018. Two first-floor wings available. Potential for five to nine year lease. Highly efficient floor plan. Shell condition with improvement allowance available. Clubhouse featuring a fitness center, kitchen facility, and meeting space. 6.4/1000 parking.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located within Colonial TownPark, Orlando’s premier mixed-use development, featuring quality retail, restaurants, banking, hotels and apartments - all within walking distance; Redundant power sources; I-4 visibility; Easy access to I-4 and the Greenway (417-toll); 4.25/1,000 parking.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Fitness Center w/ separate shower and locker facilities
Natures Table Café with indoor and outdoor seating
3,000 USF conference/training room (divisible into two rooms)
Dual-feed electrical service from two (2) separate substations via a redundant loop
Direct access on Interstate 4 and SR 417 and soon to be completed SR 429 (eastern and western beltway)

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Colonial Center 600 is located within Colonial TownPark, Orlando's premier mixed-use development featuring walkable high-quality retail, restaurants, banking, office, multi-family and access to walking trails and a community park.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: SUBLEASE OPPORTUNITY AT LAKE MARY’S NORTHPOINT CENTER BUSINESS DISTRICT

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Heathrow International Business Center is located within a 370-acre office park and offers a full-service Marriott Hotel, retail, banking, a 9-acre park and bike and running trails. The office park allows for easy access to I-4 and the Greenway (417-toll).

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Four-story Class A building. Fitness center with lockers and showers (Building 400; available to Building 300 tenants). On-site management. Adjacent to Heathrow Country Club, executive housing and luxury apartments. Ample on-site surface parking.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Located on the Greens of Heathrow Country Club
